  "summary": {
    "en": "A 100-piece creative fort kit for tents, secret bases, dome shapes, and family gift projects.",
    "zh": "100件创意堡垒拼搭套装，适合帐篷、秘密基地、圆顶造型和家庭礼品项目。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 100-piece set gives children enough parts to build compact tents, house frames, domes, and multi-bay play spaces.",
      "Lightweight PP rods and connector balls make assembly approachable for family use, classroom play, and retail demonstrations.",
      "The gift-style box and storage bag support e-commerce sales, holiday programs, and branded promotional bundles.",
      "Standard and glow-style options can be adapted for OEM/ODM projects, including color matching and packaging updates."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "100件配置可支持儿童搭建小型帐篷、房屋框架、圆顶结构和多分区游戏空间。",
      "轻便PP杆件与连接球让家庭、课堂和零售演示场景中的拼搭更容易上手。",
      "礼品化彩盒和收纳袋适合电商销售、节日项目和品牌促销组合。",
      "可根据OEM/ODM需求调整普通款或夜光款，包括配色和包装方案。"
    ]
  },
